---
// Closing punchline + signed letter + minimal links. The "0"
// counter is the screenshot-bait moment.
---

<footer class="px-6 pt-32 pb-16 border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- The closing punchline. Editorial, big, simple. -->
    <div class="mb-24 md:mb-32 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-8">
        Bytes Pace sent off your Mac today
      </p>
      <div
        class="pace-display text-[var(--color-positive)] tracking-tighter"
        style="font-size: clamp(7rem, 22vw, 18rem); line-height: 0.85;"
        aria-label="Zero"
      >
        0
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 pace-margin-note text-base md:text-lg">
        Same number tomorrow.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Signed letter, full-width, with hanging indent like a real
         letter would have. -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto pace-prose mb-20">
      <p class="pace-margin-note text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-6 not-italic font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
        A note from me
      </p>
      <p>
        I built Pace because every assistant I tried either lived in someone
        else's data center or couldn't actually <em>do</em> anything. I wanted
        Siri's reach with a local model's privacy and a real agent's hands.
        Nobody was making it, so I did.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you try it and the third turn feels worse than I promised, email
        me directly. I'll refund you. That's the whole quality bar —
        if it's not working for you, you shouldn't be paying for it.
      </p>
      <p class="pace-display text-2xl text-white mt-8 not-italic">
        — <em>Sarthak</em>
      </p>
      <!-- TODO before launch: replace the placeholder below with the
           real product support address (e.g. sarthak@<your domain>).
           Until then this link is intentionally absent. -->
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom-of-page chrome — keep it minimal, no four-column
         link grid. -->
    <div
      class="border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white">
        <span class="inline-flex items-end gap-[3px] h-5 w-6 text-[var(--color-accent)]" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="pace-bar h-3"></span>
          <span class="pace-bar h-5"></span>
          <span class="pace-bar h-4"></span>
          <span class="pace-bar h-3"></span>
        </span>
        <span class="font-semibold">Pace</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] ml-2 hidden md:inline">·</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-xs hidden md:inline">made for macOS in California</span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-xs">
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Terms</a>
        <!-- TODO: add `<a href="mailto:YOUR_EMAIL">Email</a>` once
             the support address is finalized. -->
        <span>© 2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
